      <title>中国实际借贷成本飙升将拖累2024年经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/china-s-surging-real-borrowing-costs-to-drag-on-growth-into-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于通货紧缩压力挥之不去，且央行可能会避免大幅降息，预计 2024 年中国的实际借贷成本将保持在高位，这对经济增长构成又一个威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/china-s-surging-real-borrowing-costs-to-drag-on-growth-into-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 06:35:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
